node.text: This Christmas my friends and I planned an extreme Santa as a little way to bring joy and help families in need that have been effected by corona. Thank you so much for everyone who donated and helped make this project happen 🎁🎄 Merry Christmas everyone. @maximignite @thelocalloveclub @influencingkindness @theflowstatevisuals @thehostsgroup @lesliehannahbelle

node.title: Flying the helicopter to drop Santa to deliver toys to kids in need 🎄🎁

node.text:
Turning 25 tomorrow 🎂 
reflecting on the past amazing year. Ageing is such a beautiful thing, another year wiser, more cultured, closer to my long term goals and learning who I am each and everyday.
